%h2 Contact the Seller

If you are interested in purchasing this book, please fill out this form and send an email to the seller.

= form_tag commit_buy_posting_path("#{@posting.id}"), :id => "buyer_info_form", :method => :post do

  %p
    = label :email, :buyer_email, 'Your e-mail:'
    = text_field :email, :buyer_email, :class => "required email"
  
  %p
    = label :email, :body, 'Message to the seller:'
    %br
    = text_area :email, :body, :size => "80x5", :class => "required"
    
  %p
    = submit_tag 'Send'
    
